<item>
            <title>[SOLR-17860] DocBasedVersionConstraintsProcessorFactory does not support PULL replicas</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-17860</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the &lt;tt&gt;DocBasedVersionConstraintsProcessorFactory&lt;/tt&gt; cannot be used with Pull Replicas because it has a very old check to make sure that the Core has an UpdateLog configured. Since the &lt;tt&gt;DocBasedVersionConstraintsProcessorFactory&lt;/tt&gt; should be able to handle only doing the necessary logic on the leader, this check can be skipped for non-leader-eligible replicas (PULL).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
