                            <comment id="18016543" author="dsmiley" created="Wed, 27 Aug 2025 12:59:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m surprised this was put in a patch release... it strikes me as borderline improvement vs bug.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="18016587" author="houston" created="Wed, 27 Aug 2025 16:27:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oh wow that&apos;s crazy flaky. I&apos;ll look into it and fix it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As for bug/improvement. This very much feels like a bug with an easy fix to me, since it certainly wasn&apos;t the original idea to not support PULL replicas with this URP. And since the fix is fairly safe (tests not withstanding), I think including it in 9.9.1 (if it ever comes out) is reasonable.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But I&apos;m happy to revert on branch_9_9 if others disagree.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
